dct_title_s: Cape Fear River, from entrance to Reeves Point
dct_description_sm: triangulation by C.P. Bolles, A.S. Wadsworth, and D.B. Wainwright ; topography by C.P. Bolles, C.T. Jardella, and D.B. Wainwright ; hydrography by T.A. Jenkins ... [et al.].
Relief shown by hachures; depths shown by soundings and bathymetric shading.
"The soundings are expressed in feet and show the depth at mean low water. Depths of 18 feet and less are shown on a dotted surface."
Includes notes and tables for lights, abbreviations, and tides.
